    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Entrances to the underworld as known in any of various religions and belief systems. The gates of hell may be either apprehended in a material sense to correspond to caves or other places on earth, or conceived of in only an abstract or spiritual sense.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
